Rice production (Guinea)

Source: R/data.R
guinea_rice.Rd

Total annual rice production (million metric tons) for Guinea. 1970-2011.

Format

Annual time series of class `tsibble`.

Source

World Bank.

Examples


guinea_rice

#>  9  1978      0.440
#> 10  1979      0.460
#> # … with 32 more rows
